e.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/BLUR_LIVE_2023_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/BLUR_LIVE_2023_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/BLUR_LIVE_2023_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/BLUR_LIVE_2023_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a>昨晚（7 月 25 日星期二）在哈默史密斯的伦敦 Eventim Apollo 举行的一场亲密演出中首次推出了他们最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blur-the-ballad-of-darren-review-lyrics-tracklist-3470424">The Ballad Of Darren</a> 》中的新歌，以及一些深度剪辑和粉丝最爱的歌曲。查看下面的片段和歌单。</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/blur-every-album-ranked-3466283"><strong>阅读更多： Blur – 每张专辑均按伟大程度排列</strong></a></li></ul><p>正如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-play-the-ballad-of-darren-in-full-special-london-gig-3467326">本月早些时候宣布的</a>那样，回归的英伦流行音乐老将登上了伦敦标志性场地的舞台，完整地表演了他们的新专辑，该节目还在网上进行了直播。</p><p>乐队在弦乐四重奏的伴奏下登上舞台，贝斯手亚历克斯·詹姆斯懒洋洋地躺在沙发上抽烟，同时开始演奏专辑开场曲“The Ballad”。在从头到尾演奏新唱片的过程中，他们还首次现场现场表演了《The Everglades (For Leonard)》、《Goodbye Albert》、《Far Away Island》、《Avalon》和《The Heights》。</p><p>单曲《The Narcissist》深受观众喜爱，而下一首单曲《Barbaric》（上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-bbc-2-radio-theatre-setlist-footage-photos-watch-barbaric-3470447">在 BBC Radio 2 的一场私密伦敦演出中首次亮相</a>）也获得了不错的反响。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Blur - The Ballad，2023 年 7 月 25 日在伦敦 Hammersmith 现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gjML8PSeR8A?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊@Hammersmith Apollo |高地" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iU6vvN-hrQk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊@Hammersmith Apollo |再见阿尔伯特" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_VMdxbTCl7E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊 - 圣查尔斯广场 - 哈默史密斯阿波罗，伦敦 - 2023 年 7 月" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Nh9w8A7MURs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Blur - 自恋者在 Hammersmith Apollo 现场直播 35/07/23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mWCFOcYw-eg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊 - 野蛮 - Hammersmith Apollo，伦敦 - 2023 年 7 月" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uBasT22zxuI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Blur - Russian Strings，2023 年 7 月 25 日在伦敦 Hammersmith 现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/btB3D9GYvY0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Blur - The Everglades（献给伦纳德），2023 年 7 月 25 日在伦敦哈默史密斯现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NNmtppRuvMQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>随后乐队返回进行安可表演，这是自 2015 年以来首次演奏上一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/blurs-new-album-the-magic-whip-worth-the-wait-first-listen-review-759374">The Magic Whip</a> 》中的《Pyongyang》，这是一系列罕见的表演中的第一首。有人建议，我忘记了它的存在，”主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damon-albarn">Damon Albarn</a>在 1994 年“Parklife”专辑版本“Clover Over Dover”现场首演前说道。</p><p>接下来是“There&#39;s No Other Way”B-side“Mr Briggs”（乐队已经超过 11 年没有演奏过）、1997 年同名专辑特别版中的“All Your Life”以及现场首秀。 1994 年深受粉丝喜爱的“Parklife”b-side“虚构电影主题”。</p><p> “你还想再听一首歌吗？”在经典单曲《The Universal》的最后一次安可之前，阿尔巴恩问道，并补充道：“你想要一些不那么巧妙迟钝的东西吗？” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊 - 三叶草在多佛| 《达伦之歌》在伦敦 Eventim Apollo Hammersmith 现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/svNFRhlPPCE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="模糊“虚构电影的主题”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Wo-ciA7EEOs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CvJ1HKKIl2m/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4;