首秀）<br /> &#39;Clover Over Dover&#39;（巡演首秀；专辑版本的首次演出）<br /> &#39;先生。 Briggs&#39;（自 2012 年以来首次现场直播）<br /> &#39;你的一生&#39;<br /> “虚构电影的主题”（现场首演）<br /><em>安可2：</em><br /> “普遍”</p><p>该乐队目前凭借《The Ballad Of Darren》有望成为本周英国排名第一的歌曲，最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-two-new-blur-songs-the-rabbi-and-the-swan-3472648">分享了两首额外的新歌《The Rabbi》和《The Swan</a> 》作为豪华版的一部分。</p><p>这些独立老将现在将前往亚洲和南美演出之前参加一系列欧洲音乐节。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblur-tickets%2Fartist%2F945150" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取门票</a>和更多信息。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blur-hammersmith-apollo-ballad-darren-old-b-sides-rarities-setlist-footage-watch-3473677">Blur 首次现场表演新歌，并在 Hammersmith 亲密演出中首次表演罕见的深度剪辑，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 S Club 发行 20 年来首张单曲《These Are The Days》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-release-first-single-in-20-years-with-these-are-the-days-listen-3473621?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= s-club 发行 20 年来第一张单曲，与这些日子一起听Hollie GeraghtyWed, 26 Jul 2023 11:02:42 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3473621 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="S俱乐部" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首新歌是向今年四月去世的已故乐队成员保罗·卡特莫尔致敬</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-release-first-single-in-20-years-with-these-are-the-days-listen-3473621">S Club 发行 20 年来首张单曲《These Are The Days》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="S俱乐部" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/s-club-7-new-single-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/s-club-7">S Club</a>带着 20 年来的首张新单曲《These Are The Days》回归。</p><p>该流行乐队将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-7-reunion-tour-to-go-ahead-after-paul-cattermoles-death-3443414">今年晚些时候在第六位成员汉娜·斯皮尔里特 (Hannah Spearritt) 缺席的情况下开始重聚巡演，他们</a>将这首新歌描述为向已故乐队成员保罗·卡特莫尔 (Paul Cattermole) 致敬，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-7s-paul-cattermole-dies-aged-46-3427377">后者于今年 4 月</a>因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-7s-paul-cattermoles-cause-of-death-revealed-3445065">心脏问题</a>突然去世。</p><p>这首感伤的新歌由乐队的歌曲创作团队凯西·丹尼斯、西蒙·埃利斯、约翰·埃利斯和制作人约翰·纳撒尼尔创作，并附有一段怀旧视频，突出了乐队整个职业生涯的时刻。</p><p> “我们希望您和我们一样热爱这首歌，并与我们一起回忆您与朋友和亲人的所有最喜欢的时刻，”S Club（原 S Club 7）在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/CvJ2F77ow7U/?igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上分享道。 “这是真正的爱的劳动，一起创造它的经历是如此特别。这是给你的，保罗。”</p><p> <em>“如果有一天我们发现/我们不得不说再见（不得不说）/我们将跑回这些记忆/一次又一次地重温</em>，”他们在阳光明媚的轨道上唱道。 “<em>因为这是我们生命中的日子/我们将永远记住</em>。”</p><p>聆听“These Are The Days”并观看下面的随附视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="S 俱乐部 - 这些日子" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NEO1EdWcWFg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>早在五月，S Club 7 就确认在卡特莫尔去世后，他们今年仍将继续进行重聚巡演，但斯皮尔里特将缺席。</p><p>在他去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/s-club-7s-hannah-spearritt-pays-tribute-to-her-first-love-paul-cattermole-3432097">斯皮尔里特向她已故的乐队成员和“初恋”卡特莫尔致敬</a>。</p><p> “你可能已经注意到，今天这里只有五个人，尽管汉娜将永远是 S Club 7 的一员，但她不会参加我们这次巡演，”<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CsOt3rdoaB0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乔恩·李 (Jon Lee) 在 Instagram 视频中说道</a>，在该视频中，成员们明显情绪激动。 “我们祝愿她未来一切顺利。不过，我们五个人真的很兴奋，也做好了准备。”</p><p>他们还将其重新命名为“Good Times Tour”，以纪念已故的乐队成员，他在乐队的同名歌曲中担任主唱，他计划在巡演中表演这首歌。</p><p>蒂娜·巴雷特表示，他们的乐队成员的去世“现在真的很难接受”，而布拉德利·麦金托什补充说，乐队仍然“难以置信”失去他们的“老大哥”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CqvRBuWIvEl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 5