 《赛博朋克 2077》开发商 CD Projekt Red 裁减“约 100 名”员工https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-cd-projekt-red-drops-around-100-staff-3473656?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cyberpunk-2077-developer- cd-projekt-red-drops-around-100-staffImogen Donovan Wed, 26 Jul 2023 10:26:16 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3473656 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这些裁员不会是“立即”的</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-cd-projekt-red-drops-around-100-staff-3473656">《赛博朋克 2077》开发商 CD Projekt Red 裁员“约 100 名”员工的</a>消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cyberpunk-2077">《赛博朋克 2077》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-witcher-3-wild-hunt"><em>《巫师》</em></a>游戏的波兰开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt-red">CD Projekt Red</a>宣布将解雇“约 100 名”员工。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/its-a-golden-age-for-music-collaborations-in-gaming-3383562">这是游戏音乐合作的黄金时代</a></strong></li></ul><p>首席执行官亚当·基辛斯基 (Adam Kiciński) 在其官方网站上发布的<a href="https://www.cdprojekt.com/en/media/news/cd-projekt-red-organizational-update/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">组织更新</a>中表示：“这很难说，但今天我们人太多了。” “我们有才华横溢的人员正在完成他们的任务，并且根据当前和预期的项目需求，我们已经知道明年我们没有其他机会给他们。”</p><p>首席执行官解释说，裁员不会“立即”进行，一些员工将留在工作室直到 2024 年第一财季。此外，CD Projekt Red 没有透露哪些部门将受到损失的影响。 “大约 100 人”，即公司员工的“大约 9%”将被解雇。 </p><figure id="attachment_3473680" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473680" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473680" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/quantum-error-no-ps4-version-comparison2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473680" class="wp-caption-text"> 《赛博朋克 2077》图片来源：CD Projekt Red</figcaption></figure><p> Kiciński confirmed that these employees will have “ample time to process and adjust to the change” and a “comprehensive severance package” will reflect the work they&#39;ve contributed to CD Projekt Red during their time there.</p><p> Late last year, CD Projekt Red announced that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-will-get-a-game-of-the-year-edition-3360816">there is a <em>Cyberpunk 2077</em> Game of the Year edition</a> to be released after the arrival of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-sequel-director-phantom-liberty-3456353"><em>Phantom Liberty</em> DLC</a> .</p><p> As well as this, the developer revealed that there are <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/two-new-the-witcher-spin-off-games-are-on-the-way-3323121">two new Witcher entries in the works</a> . Currently codenamed Canis Majoris and Sirius, these are spin-offs in the series as development on <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/witcher-4-pre-production-3235403-3235403"><em>The Witcher 4</em></a> started in March 2022.</p><p> In other gaming news, upcoming horror <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/quantum-error"><em>Quantum Error</em></a> will <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/quantum-error-skipping-ps4-because-it-isnt-fair-on-players-3473606">not be launching on PlayStation 4 anymore</a> as a result of the significant technical superiority of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a> version.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cyberpunk-2077-developer-cd-projekt-red-drops-around-100-staff-3473656">&#39;Cyberpunk 2077&#39; developer CD Projekt Red drops “around 100” staff</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Hugh Grant's casting in 'Wonka' criticised by actor with dwarfism https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grants-casting-wonka-criticised-by-actor-with-dwarfism-3473659?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hugh-grants-casting-wonka-criticised-by-actor-with-dwarfismAdam Starkey Wed, 26 Jul 2023 10:13:52 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3473659 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hugh Grant Wonka" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “A lot of actors [with dwarfism] feel like we are being pushed out of the industry we love”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grants-casting-wonka-criticised-by-actor-with-dwarfism-3473659">Hugh Grant&#39;s casting in &#39;Wonka&#39; criticised by actor with dwarfism</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Hugh Grant Wonka" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hugh-grant-wonka-new-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> An actor with dwarfism has criticised the casting of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-grant">Hugh Grant</a> as an Oompa Loompa in <em>Wonka</em> .</p><p> Directed by Paul King ( <em>Paddington</em> ), the upcoming film is based on the universe created in Roald Dahl&#39;s 1964 novel <em>Charlie And The Chocolate Factory</em> . Timothée Chalamet plays the lead role of Willy Wonka, in what&#39;s billed as a prequel to the 1971 film adaptation.</p><p> George Coppen, who is best known for playing Sweet Cupid in <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix&#39;s</a> <em>The School For Good And Evil</em> , believes the Oompa Loompa role should have been given to an actor with dwarfism.</p><p> Speaking to the <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-derbyshire-66302072" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC</em></a> , Coppen said: “A lot of actors [with dwarfism] feel like we are being pushed out of the industry we love. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="旺卡 |官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/otNh9bTjXWg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “A lot of people, myself included, argue that dwarfs should be offered everyday roles in dramas and soaps, but we aren&#39;t getting offered those roles. One door is being closed but they have forgotten to open the next one.”</p><p> Speaking about the depiction of Grant&#39;s Oompa Loompa, as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wonka-trailer-timothee-chalamet-roald-dahl-hugh-grant-oompa-loompa-3467341">shown in the first trailer</a> , Coppen added: “They&#39;ve enlarged his head so his head looks bigger. [I thought] what the hell have you done to him?”</p><p> In both 1971&#39;s <em>Willy Wonka &amp; The Chocolate Factory</em> , starring Gene Wilder, and 2005&#39;s <em>Charlie And The Chocolate Factory</em> with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-depp">Johnny Depp</a> , the Oompa Loompa&#39;s were all played by actors with dwarfism.</p><p> <em>NME</em> has reached out to Warner Bros. for comment.</p><p> <em>Wonka</em> – which follows a younger version of the titular character – also stars Keegan Michael-Key, Paterson Joseph, Matt Lucas, Mathew Baynton, Sally Hawkins and Rowan Atkinson.</p><p> <em>Wonka</em> is scheduled to be released in cinemas on December 15, 2023.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hugh-grants-casting-wonka-criticised-by-actor-with-dwarfism-3473659">Hugh Grant&#39;s casting in &#39;Wonka&#39; criticised by actor with dwarfism</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
